---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section id="flota" class="relative py-28 lg:py-40 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-surface via-brand/[0.02] to-surface dark:from-surface-dark dark:via-brand/[0.03] dark:to-surface-dark" />
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
          Nuestra <span class="text-brand">Flota</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted dark:text-muted-dark leading-relaxed max-w-[50ch]">
          Camiones de carga con capacidad de 17, 18 y 20 metros cúbicos para entregar tu pedido directo a la obra.
        </p>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border dark:border-border-dark">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-brand/10 dark:bg-brand/5">
                <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Capacidad</th>
                <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Ideal para</th>
                <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Uso recomendado</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
              <tr class="hover:bg-brand/[0.02] transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4 font-bold text-brand">17 mt³</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Accesos ajustados</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Obra pequeña, calles estrechas</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="hover:bg-brand/[0.02] transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4 font-bold text-brand">18 mt³</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Obra residencial</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Casas, edificios, urbanizaciones</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="hover:bg-brand/[0.02] transition-colors">
                <td class="p-4 font-bold text-brand">20 mt³</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Gran volumen</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Proyectos grandes, carreteras, naves</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative p-1.5 rounded-[2rem] bg-gradient-to-b from-brand/20 to-transparent lg:sticky lg:top-28">
        <div class="rounded-[calc(2rem-0.375rem)] overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark">
          <div class="relative">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565947256685-e8089e88ddda?fm=jpg&q=80&w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
              srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565947256685-e8089e88ddda?fm=jpg&q=80&w=400 400w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565947256685-e8089e88ddda?fm=jpg&q=80&w=800 800w"
              sizes="(max-width:768px) 100vw, 600px"
              alt="Camión de volteo"
              class="aspect-[4/3] w-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
